I visited the restaurant located in downtown Tampa. This place is just horribly dirty. The floor was dirty, the tables were dirty,  & worst yet the restroom were dirty! This restaurant could have earned a one star rating by the condition of the restroom alone. The sink faucet was encrusted with a combination of algae & calcium deposits. The sink was backed up with some sort of brown liquid. The toilet was marred & dirty from God knows what. All but one light was out & that one working one was flickering. This felt like it could have been the set of a SAW movie. I went in to wash my hands but to be honest I think my hands were cleaner before entering that purgatory. Hmmm, I wonder if this place is a stopover on your way to hell?
